# My GitHub Projects
### Moebius Project
[Click here to play the Moebius Project](http://enigmaticagh.github.io/Hookshot/Hookshot.html)  
This is a simple infinite runner where you assume the role of a frog and have to get as far as you can. Use your tongue to stick to objects and swing through the jungle! This game is still in early development.  

### IGS 2 Project
[Click here to play the IGS 2 Project](https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/10679993/Unity%20Web%20Player/IGS2/IGS2.html)  
This is currently just a prototype.
